This essay will express my thinkings of the popular topic in the year 2026 -getting more than one job with its benefits and loss.

The profits for getting 2 or more jobs is quite obvious, which is you get more money. Since economics and price are getting higher and higher. Those extra jobs will be one of the crutials things to live in this society. However, if we still have only one job, we will not live a happy life unless the job pocesses high salary. For example, not a small ammount of people will face extremely unreasonable rental fee that costs you 1 month of your salary while you are only allowed to stay for a month, people in this era have to get multiple jobs just to cut ends off. Therefore, it is better to get a few more jobs.

However, things are like a double-edged sword, having a good side and a bad side. the disadvantages are both the mental losses and phisical loss. Specifically, mass amount of people exchanged your power or emotions for money, and all people can do is just barely living in this cruel society. Therefore, a lot of still need to consider about your body strengtheness. For example, people who gets too tired will go to the hospital unless they are tired of their lifes, the salary will not be even enough to cover the bills. 

In conclution, don't do what you can't afford. Or it is a better choice to focus on a better job instead of getting multiple jobs. 